l.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 LIVE!\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB bronze in mixed triathlon relay; cycling begins; day 10 latest from Paris  Team GB have already picked up 37 medals across the first nine days of the Games, including 10 gold medals.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.8336506985439417e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999987294359, \"rank\": 1.2704361691199525e-09, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team currently sit at fifth place on the medal table.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a British gold on the water on day eight in the men's rowing, as well as the day before when Emily Craig and Imogen Grant won the women's lightweight double sculls.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9991202946875957, \"rank\": 0.0007379702183399784, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Craig\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emily Craig\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Craig\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Craig\"}, {\"begi